    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we're committed to giving you a complete and honest picture before you make any decisions. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 you may notice a few light scratches or minor scuffs consistent with normal everyday use, but there are no significant dents, rust, or structural concerns. The paint retains a healthy shine and the body panels are straight and solid. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-kept; the upholstery shows modest wear on the driver's seat and high-touch areas, but nothing that detracts from comfort or usability. All major features and controls function as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and reliably, with no warning lights or known mechanical issues. The tires have good tread remaining and the brakes are in serviceable condition. This is a dependable, everyday vehicle that has been looked after and is ready for its next owner without requiring immediate repairs or significant investment.",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in good condition, and prospective buyers can expect a reliable, well-maintained option that shows normal signs of use but remains in solid overall shape. The exterior presents minor cosmetic wear consistent with regular daily driving \u2014 small scuffs or light scratches may be visible upon close inspection, but there is no significant body damage, rust, or major paint issues. The interior is clean and functional, with expected wear on high-contact surfaces such as the steering wheel, seat bolsters, and pedals, but nothing that detracts from everyday comfort or usability. Mechanically, the vehicle runs well and has been maintained; buyers should still expect to perform routine upkeep as with any used vehicle of this age and mileage. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and electronics \u2014 are in working order. This is a practical, honest purchase for a buyer seeking dependable transportation at a fair price, without the premium of a mint-condition vehicle.",
      "price": 35000.0,
